feat: Implement comment notification system
- Added SendCommentNotification method to EmailService for notifying users about new comments and replies. - Enhanced EmailService with new email templates for comment notifications. - Introduced CommentNotificationJob to handle the asynchronous sending of comment notifications. - Updated Broker to dispatch comment notification jobs. - Refactored Comment model to include status and notification settings. - Created DTOs for comment creation and response structures. - Updated repositories to handle new comment data structures and methods. - Improved error handling and logging for comment-related operations.
